title: Extra brown bin collections trialled in Wellingborough (Wellingborough Borough Council)
text: ( Source : Wellingborough Borough Council ) Wellingborough Council will collect garden waste for one extra month this year due to popular demand for the service. The fortnightly brown bin collections will continue into November, before pausing
